### 3.9 输出 Schema 标准化【新增】

> ⚡ **工程化关键**：各 Agent 输出结构必须统一，Orchestrator 才能正确汇聚

```python
# output_schemas.py
from pydantic import BaseModel

class LegalAnalysisOutput(BaseModel):
    agent_name: str
    confidence_level: str  # GREEN|YELLOW|RED|GRAY
    legal_basis: list[str]  # ["《民法典》第X条", ...]
    analysis: str
    uncertain_items: list[str]  # 待律师核实项
    recommendations: list[str]
    requires_attorney_review: bool  # 触发审查门控

class CaseInfoOutput(BaseModel):
    parties: dict
    timeline: list[dict]  # [{date, fact, evidence}]
    evidence_list: list[dict]
    claim_labels: list[str]
    missing_info: list[dict]  # [{category, question, impact}]

class StatuteOutput(BaseModel):
    deadlines: list[dict]  # [{type, start_date, deadline, days_remaining, urgency}]
    most_urgent: dict
    alerts: list[str]
```

